  Owns:

  - Manifest permissions
  - Side panel entry point
  - Canvas domain setup
  - Canvas route detection
  - Non-Canvas empty state

  Relevant PRD areas:

  - Goals and constraints: canvas-lms-extension-prd.md:11
  - Canvas detection: canvas-lms-extension-prd.md:249
